Tk::DateEntry Module

Tk::DateEntry is an Entry widget with a drop-down calendar, allowing the
user to select a date by clicking in the calendar.

To install, type

	$ perl Makefile.PL
	$ make
	$ make test
	$ make install

On Windows systems, use dmake or nmake instead of make.

For a demonstration you can use

	$ make demo

DateEntry.pm contains pod documentation.

Send bug reports, comments and suggestions to slaven@rezic.de
